TextEng: Excuse me, my <lord/lady>, but I'm simply waiting for... ah... someone.
Text: 실례지만 나리, 전... 그냥 누군가를 기다리고 있어서요.

TextEng: I've no time to speak, my <lord/lady>. Excuse me.
Text: 말씀 나눌 시간이 없습니다, 나리. 실례합니다.

TextEng: Good day to you, my <lady/lord>.
Text: 좋은 하루 되십시오, 나리.

TextEng: Do not come too near, peasant! It's bad enough that I have to come to such a dreadful place!
Text: 너무 가까이 오지 마, 천민아! 이런 끔찍한 곳에 와야 하는 것만도 충분히 괴로워!

TextEng: Excuse me, peasant... I've more important matters to attend to.
Text: 실례지만, 천민... 더 중요한 일이 있어서 말이야.

TextEng: Do not speak to me. I've not come for the company, I can assure you.
Text: 말 걸지 마. 친목 도모하러 온 게 아니니까, 확실히 말해두지.

TextEng: You're not a contestant, are you? No... I don't think I've ever seen you.
Text: 참가자는 아니겠지? 아니... 본 적이 없는 것 같은데.

TextEng: Rather a titillating little sport, don't you think?
Text: 꽤 짜릿한 작은 스포츠 아닌가?

TextEng: Have you entered the dungeon? No, you're a nobody, I see.
Text: 던전에 들어갔나? 아니지, 보아하니 아무것도 아닌 사람이군.

TextEng: Excuse me, but I'm rather wrapped up in the proceedings.
Text: 실례지만, 경기에 빠져 있어서 말이야.

TextEng: I've no time to talk, dear <man/woman>.
Text: 얘기 나눌 시간 없네, 친구.

TextEng: I saw you in the dungeon earlier, my <lord/lady>. Quite impressive.
Text: 아까 던전에서 봤습니다, 나리. 꽤 인상적이더군요.

TextEng: Do you think you might be re-entering soon? I've a wager on you.
Text: 곧 다시 들어갈 생각인가요? 당신한테 거는 내기가 있거든요.

TextEng: Too bad you left so soon. I was interested in your progress.
Text: 너무 일찍 나왔네요. 당신 진행상황이 궁금했는데.

TextEng: Ha! I knew you would leave the dungeon! Nobody's made it, yet.
Text: 하! 던전에서 나올 줄 알았어! 아직 아무도 성공 못 했으니까.

TextEng: You show marvelous skills, dear <man/woman>. It's a good thing you didn't die in there.
Text: 놀라운 실력을 보여주셨군요, 친구. 안에서 죽지 않아서 다행이에요.

TextEng: You completed the dungeon! Astounding! Absolutely amazing!
Text: 던전을 완료했어! 놀라워! 정말 대단해!

TextEng: Hurrah for the hero! Tell us a first-hand account of your victory, yes?
Text: 영웅 만세! 승리의 생생한 이야기 좀 들려주지 않겠나?

TextEng: I won quite the wager on you, my <lord/lady>! Bravo! Bra-vo!!
Text: 당신 덕에 내기에서 꽤 땄습니다, 나리! 브라보! 브라보!!

TextEng: So you won half of Mutamin's fortune, did you? You earned it, my <lord/lady>!
Text: 그래서 무타민 재산의 절반을 땄다고요? 그럴 자격이 있습니다, 나리!

TextEng: It was quite exciting to watch you finish! Congratulations!
Text: 완주하는 걸 보니 정말 흥분되더군! 축하합니다!
